<font color="#787878">Anyone could be next.</font>

782
01:06:39,704 --> 01:06:42,332
<font color="#787878">It could be you. Understand?</font>

783
01:06:42,499 --> 01:06:43,967
<font color="#787878">Nobody's safe.</font>

784
01:06:44,125 --> 01:06:45,672
<font color="#787878">What are you talking about?</font>

785
01:06:47,962 --> 01:06:50,681
<font color="#787878">We weren't supposed to survive
that bridge collapse.</font>

786
01:06:50,840 --> 01:06:53,719
<font color="#787878">And so now it's kill or be killed.</font>

787
01:06:54,302 --> 01:06:56,475
<font color="#787878">You get that, Dennis?</font>

788
01:06:57,597 --> 01:06:58,644
<font color="#787878">Whatever.</font>

789
01:06:58,806 --> 01:07:01,650
<font color="#787878">I warned you.
Do whatever you wanna do.</font>

790
01:07:05,480 --> 01:07:07,198
<font color="#787878">I will.</font>

791
01:07:11,986 --> 01:07:14,284
<font color="#787878">Hey, Agent Block, it's Dennis. Um....</font>

792
01:07:14,447 --> 01:07:18,372
<font color="#787878">Listen, Pete just came in here
and he's just completely lost it.</font>

793
01:07:18,535 --> 01:07:21,414
<font color="#787878">He's yelling about "kill or be killed."</font>

794
01:07:21,579 --> 01:07:24,503
<font color="#787878">Oh, yeah,
it definitely sounded like a threat.</font>

795
01:07:41,474 --> 01:07:42,566
<font color="#787878">What happened?</font>

796
01:07:42,725 --> 01:07:45,649
<font color="#787878">~ I don't know. I don't know.
~ It just happened so fast.</font>

797
01:07:45,812 --> 01:07:48,531
<font color="#787878">~ Nathan. Are you okay?
~ Yeah.</font>

798
01:07:48,690 --> 01:07:52,365
<font color="#787878">~ We heard, and we thought....
~ No. No, uh, I'm good.</font>

799
01:07:53,486 --> 01:07:54,738
<font color="#787878">Did you kill him?</font>

800
01:07:55,113 --> 01:07:56,239
<font color="#787878">What?</font>

801
01:07:56,406 --> 01:07:59,000
<font color="#787878">No. No, I just....</font>

802
01:07:59,158 --> 01:08:02,037
<font color="#787878">It was just timing, you know?
He got in the way and....</font>

803
01:08:02,203 --> 01:08:03,500
<font color="#787878">No, you did, didn't you?</font>

804
01:08:03,663 --> 01:08:07,042
<font color="#787878">You saw it coming, and then you took his life. You put him in the way.</font>

805
01:08:07,208 --> 01:08:08,835
<font color="#787878">No, I didn't really do anything.</font>

806
01:08:09,002 --> 01:08:11,846
<font color="#787878">~ Did you or didn't you?
~ Hey, Peter, calm down.</font>

807
01:08:12,005 --> 01:08:13,382
<font color="#787878">Did you or didn't you?</font>

808
01:08:16,217 --> 01:08:18,265
<font color="#787878">Did you or didn't you?</font>

809
01:08:19,178 --> 01:08:22,102
<font color="#787878">Yes. I think I did.</font>

810
01:08:22,932 --> 01:08:24,184
<font color="#787878">I killed him.</font>

811
01:08:25,101 --> 01:08:28,275
<font color="#787878">So if the theory works,
then you traded spots.</font>

812
01:08:28,438 --> 01:08:32,113
<font color="#787878">He should have your death,
and you should have his years.</font>

813
01:08:32,859 --> 01:08:34,156
<font color="#787878">How do we know for sure?</font>

814
01:08:34,319 --> 01:08:36,196
<font color="#787878">I think there's an order to these deaths.</font>

815
01:08:37,614 --> 01:08:40,584
<font color="#787878">They mirror the order everyone died in on the bridge.</font>

816
01:08:40,742 --> 01:08:42,540
<font color="#787878">Then who would be next?</font>

817
01:08:44,370 --> 01:08:46,623
<font color="#787878">Who wants to be first to tell me
what the hell happened?</font>

818
01:08:47,081 --> 01:08:48,128
<font color="#787878">Who is it, Sam?</font>

819
01:08:48,291 --> 01:08:49,338
<font color="#787878">Who's what?</font>

820
01:08:54,631 --> 01:08:57,134
<font color="#787878">Dennis! It was Dennis.</font>

821
01:08:57,592 --> 01:08:59,560
<font color="#787878">No shit.</font>

822
01:09:00,595 --> 01:09:02,347
<font color="#787878">Jesus.</font>

823
01:09:05,600 --> 01:09:07,443
<font color="#787878">Why are you fighting me on this?</font>

824
01:09:07,602 --> 01:09:09,980
<font color="#787878">You're not seriously going to work, are you?</font>

825
01:09:10,146 --> 01:09:14,447
<font color="#787878">Molly, Isaac died on a massage table.</font>

826
01:09:14,609 --> 01:09:17,283
<font color="#787878">If Death is gonna come for me,
I don't think it matters where I am.</font>

827
01:09:17,445 --> 01:09:19,197
<font color="#787878">You have to do something.</font>

828
01:09:19,364 --> 01:09:22,083
<font color="#787878">~ What, kill someone so I can live?
~ No, of course not.</font>

829
01:09:22,867 --> 01:09:24,995
<font color="#787878">We'll just have to
figure something else out.</font>

830
01:09:25,161 --> 01:09:27,255
<font color="#787878">I have figured it out.</font>

831
01:09:27,705 --> 01:09:30,675
<font color="#787878">Something saved me on that bridge.</font>

832
01:09:30,833 --> 01:09:32,676
<font color="#787878">Maybe it doesn't want me to die.</font>

833
01:09:35,004 --> 01:09:36,472
<font color="#787878">Maybe.</font>

834
01:09:36,631 --> 01:09:39,510
<font color="#787878">We can't live our lives in fear, Moll.</font>

835
01:09:41,886 --> 01:09:46,187
<font color="#787878">So if it happens tomorrow,
or 50 years from now, whatever.</font>

836
01:09:46,349 --> 01:09:48,568
<font color="#787878">As long as we're together....</font>

837
01:09:49,811 --> 01:09:51,028
<font color="#787878">I'll be okay.</font>

838
01:09:53,731 --> 01:09:56,575
<font color="#787878">Right? Why don't you come by
after my shift....</font>

839
01:09:56,734 --> 01:09:58,828
<font color="#787878">and I'll make you
a nice late dinner, okay?</font>

840
01:10:07,620 --> 01:10:08,963
<font color="#787878">All right, give me this.</font>

841
01:10:17,922 --> 01:10:20,175
<font color="#787878">~ Excuse me.
~ We don't have to wait for them, do we?</font>

842
01:10:20,341 --> 01:10:22,639
<font color="#787878">~ I'll let you know.
~ Okay, thank you.</font>

843
01:10:25,471 --> 01:10:27,815
<font color="#787878">To the girl on the run</font>

844
01:10:38,359 --> 01:10:39,827
<font color="#787878">Veal's ready, take it out.</font>

845
01:10:39,986 --> 01:10:42,080
<font color="#787878">Samuel. Get to work on the bourguignon.</font>

846
01:10:50,413 --> 01:10:51,630
<font color="#787878">Whoa.</font>

847
01:10:52,039 --> 01:10:53,086
<font color="#787878">Pan coming through.</font>

848
01:10:54,709 --> 01:10:56,382
<font color="#787878">Whoa, watch yourself.</font>

849
01:11:07,138 --> 01:11:09,482
<font color="#787878">~ Okay. Meat's in. Pick it up, eh?
~ Yes, sir.</font>

850
01:11:20,359 --> 01:11:22,032
<font color="#787878">Whoa.</font>

851
01:11:22,195 --> 01:11:24,038
<font color="#787878">That could've been ugly, huh? Ha, ha.</font>

852
01:11:24,197 --> 01:11:26,871
<font color="#787878">Yeah. Could've been.</font>

853
01:11:31,871 --> 01:11:33,248
<font color="#787878">Vincent, speed it up, okay?</font>

854
01:11:40,588 --> 01:11:41,885
<font color="#787878">Whoa, hey!</font>

855
01:12:05,446 --> 01:12:07,448
<font color="#787878">Hey, clean that grate.</font>

856
01:12:15,915 --> 01:12:18,919
<font color="#787878">~ Just met your girlfriend.
~ Oh.</font>

857
01:12:19,085 --> 01:12:22,009
<font color="#787878">Are you sure it's okay
if I make her a little something?</font>

858
01:12:22,630 --> 01:12:24,678
<font color="#787878">Make sure to clean up afterward.</font>

859
01:12:24,841 --> 01:12:27,594
<font color="#787878">I will, of course. Thank you.</font>

860
01:12:28,886 --> 01:12:30,263
<font color="#787878">And, chef....</font>

861
01:12:31,848 --> 01:12:33,725
<font color="#787878">The apprenticeship.</font>

862
01:12:33,891 --> 01:12:36,394
<font color="#787878">If the offer still stands....</font>

863
01:12:36,561 --> 01:12:37,904
<font color="#787878">I'd like to take it.</font>

864
01:12:39,564 --> 01:12:41,066
<font color="#787878">It's yours.</font>

865
01:12:55,788 --> 01:12:57,256
<font color="#787878">Okay, no more suspense.</font>

866
01:12:59,041 --> 01:13:01,089
<font color="#787878">What you've been waiting for.</font>

867
01:13:02,837 --> 01:13:05,306
<font color="#787878">Wow. You're gonna help me
with this, right?</font>

868
01:13:05,464 --> 01:13:06,932
<font color="#787878">Yeah, sure, if you want me to....</font>

869
01:13:07,091 --> 01:13:08,593
<font color="#787878">No? You don't want me to....?</font>

870
01:13:09,385 --> 01:13:10,557
<font color="#787878">So how's your French?</font>

871
01:13:11,053 --> 01:13:13,306
<font color="#787878">Heh. Terrible.</font>

872
01:13:13,472 --> 01:13:17,147
<font color="#787878">Oh, good. Well, then,
we can be terrible together.</font>

873
01:13:17,310 --> 01:13:20,484
<font color="#787878">~ Why?
~ I took the internship.</font>

874
01:13:20,646 --> 01:13:24,571
<font color="#787878">What? Sam, that's amazing.</font>

875
01:13:27,945 --> 01:13:29,743
<font color="#787878">I'm so proud of you.</font>

876
01:13:46,923 --> 01:13:49,676
<font color="#787878">~ Peter.
~ Hey.</font>

877
01:13:51,469 --> 01:13:54,518
<font color="#787878">You okay, man?
You look a little, uh, upset.</font>

878
01:13:54,680 --> 01:13:58,605
<font color="#787878">Yeah. Yeah, yeah, yeah.
Just a rough couple days.</font>

879
01:13:59,310 --> 01:14:01,984
<font color="#787878">Yeah. Yeah, for everyone.</font>

880
01:14:02,939 --> 01:14:04,816
<font color="#787878">For some more than others.</font>

881
01:14:05,608 --> 01:14:07,030
<font color="#787878">Do you mind if I come in?</font>

882
01:14:07,193 --> 01:14:09,537
<font color="#787878">Oh, yeah, of course. Yeah, come in.</font>

883
01:14:15,201 --> 01:14:16,703
<font color="#787878">Here, have a seat.</font>

884
01:14:17,536 --> 01:14:19,129
<font color="#787878">Thanks.</font>

885
01:14:23,292 --> 01:14:24,544
<font color="#787878">Hey, Peter.</font>

886
01:14:25,711 --> 01:14:27,509
<font color="#787878">Hi, Molly.</font>

887
01:14:42,311 --> 01:14:46,111
<font color="#787878">Peter, can I get you anything to eat? I can make you up some pasta.</font>

888
01:14:46,732 --> 01:14:50,236
<font color="#787878">Uh, no. No, no, no. I'm good.
Uh, thank you.</font>

889
01:14:51,737 --> 01:14:53,580
<font color="#787878">Uh, I'm sorry. I just thought....</font>

890
01:14:53,739 --> 01:14:56,333
<font color="#787878">It's good that you're here.
You shouldn't be alone right now.</font>

891
01:14:56,951 --> 01:14:59,420
<font color="#787878">Yeah, you know,
I'm surprised I'm here at all.</font>

892
01:15:00,830 --> 01:15:02,252
<font color="#787878">Uh....</font>

893
01:15:02,415 --> 01:15:04,258
<font color="#787878">Still alive, I mean.</font>

894
01:15:04,417 --> 01:15:05,760
<font color="#787878">I'm next to go, right?</font>

895
01:15:07,086 --> 01:15:08,759
<font color="#787878">It's me and then you, isn't it?</font>

896
01:15:11,549 --> 01:15:16,396
<font color="#787878">Anyways, uh, I was up all last night, you know....</font>

897
01:15:16,554 --> 01:15:19,728
<font color="#787878">thinking about if I could really do it.</font>

898
01:15:20,349 --> 01:15:24,149
<font color="#787878">~ Do what?
~ Take someone else's life.</font>

899
01:15:24,311 --> 01:15:29,568
<font color="#787878">If I could actually kill some stranger, replace their life with my own.</font>

900
01:15:30,526 --> 01:15:32,449
<font color="#787878">And I thought about it.</font>

901
01:15:33,237 --> 01:15:35,239
<font color="#787878">And I convinced myself that....</font>

902
01:15:36,615 --> 01:15:38,117
<font color="#787878">yeah, I could.</font>

903
01:15:40,786 --> 01:15:43,209
<font color="#787878">So I went on a walk.</font>

904
01:15:43,372 --> 01:15:46,125
<font color="#787878">You know, nowhere in particular....</font>

905
01:15:46,292 --> 01:15:49,171
<font color="#787878">but every couple of minutes,
an opportunity would just present itself</font>

906
01:15:49,336 --> 01:15:52,135
<font color="#787878">Heh. Like clockwork.</font>

907
01:15:52,548 --> 01:15:55,643
<font color="#787878">I could just grab somebody
and pull them into an alley.</font>

908
01:15:56,218 --> 01:15:59,813
<font color="#787878">Or just shove somebody off a curb
into traffic.</font>

909
01:16:00,556 --> 01:16:01,978
<font color="#787878">You know?</font>

910
01:16:02,808 --> 01:16:04,105
<font color="#787878">It'd be real easy.</font>

911
01:16:07,146 --> 01:16:09,399
<font color="#787878">Peter, what did you do?</font>

912
01:16:17,114 --> 01:16:19,537
<font color="#787878">~ Did you....?
~ No, I didn't.</font>

913
01:16:22,453 --> 01:16:24,501
<font color="#787878">I couldn't.</font>

914
01:16:24,663 --> 01:16:26,506
<font color="#787878">I realized that....</font>

915
01:16:26,665 --> 01:16:29,589
<font color="#787878">I couldn't kill somebody
that didn't deserve to die.</font>

916
01:16:31,670 --> 01:16:35,391
<font color="#787878">And I thought about Candice,
and I thought, "Wait a minute.</font>

917
01:16:36,425 --> 01:16:39,349
<font color="#787878">Candice didn't deserve to die.</font>

918
01:16:41,347 --> 01:16:44,066
<font color="#787878">Olivia didn't. Dennis didn't.</font>

919
01:16:44,850 --> 01:16:46,443
<font color="#787878">I don't."</font>

920
01:16:48,354 --> 01:16:49,651
<font color="#787878">Do I?</font>

921
01:16:49,855 --> 01:16:52,028
<font color="#787878">No, of course you don't.</font>

922
01:16:54,985 --> 01:16:56,407
<font color="#787878">Well....</font>

923
01:16:57,571 --> 01:17:03,704
<font color="#787878">none of us deserve to die,
then why is it....</font>

924
01:17:04,995 --> 01:17:07,965
<font color="#787878">that you deserve to live, Molly?</font>

925
01:17:09,875 --> 01:17:11,172
<font color="#787878">You said it yourself....</font>

926
01:17:12,378 --> 01:17:13,550
<font color="#787878">you don't.</font>

927
01:17:19,218 --> 01:17:20,640
<font color="#787878">Go!</font>

928
01:17:21,387 --> 01:17:25,938
<font color="#787878">Repeat, shots fired.
Requesting backup. 1026 Washington.</font>

929
01:17:26,684 --> 01:17:30,063
<font color="#787878">Hide and I'll distract him.
When you can, go.</font>

930
01:17:32,189 --> 01:17:33,657
<font color="#787878">Not done yet, Sam.</font>

931
01:17:36,318 --> 01:17:37,615
<font color="#787878">Where is she?</font>

932
01:17:39,655 --> 01:17:43,410
<font color="#787878">~ Where is she?!
~ I'm not gonna let you hurt her, Peter.</font>

933
01:17:43,617 --> 01:17:45,415
<font color="#787878">You're gonna have to kill me first.</font>

934
01:17:45,619 --> 01:17:47,792
<font color="#787878">Well, that doesn't do me any good. Heh, heh.</font>

935
01:17:47,955 --> 01:17:49,207
<font color="#787878">Death's after you too.</font>

936
01:17:49,373 --> 01:17:51,751
<font color="#787878">This is crazy, Peter. Don't do this.</font>

937
01:17:52,918 --> 01:17:56,513
<font color="#787878">Just think for a minute, all right?</font>

938
01:17:56,672 --> 01:17:58,265
<font color="#787878">You are not a killer.</font>

939
01:17:59,633 --> 01:18:01,260
<font color="#787878">I don't wanna kill anybody, Sam.</font>

940
01:18:04,638 --> 01:18:05,855
<font color="#787878">I don't wanna die yet either.</font>

941
01:18:12,730 --> 01:18:15,074
<font color="#787878">Heh. It's not your time yet.</font>

942
01:18:24,074 --> 01:18:26,247
<font color="#787878">Don't worry, Molly....</font>

943
01:18:28,412 --> 01:18:29,959
<font color="#787878">I didn't kill him.</font>

944
01:18:32,416 --> 01:18:36,137
<font color="#787878">But I didn't need to, Molly....</font>

945
01:18:37,213 --> 01:18:41,309
<font color="#787878">because Death
is gonna do that for me.</font>

946
01:18:41,759 --> 01:18:44,137
<font color="#787878">Doesn't mean I can't help it.</font>

947
01:18:46,096 --> 01:18:47,814
<font color="#787878">That's it.</font>

948
01:19:29,515 --> 01:19:32,735
<font color="#787878">~ Are you okay? What's going on?
~ It's Peter. He has a gun.</font>

949
01:19:37,982 --> 01:19:39,655
<font color="#787878">Oh, my God.</font>

950
01:19:43,028 --> 01:19:44,746
<font color="#787878">You killed him.</font>

951
01:19:52,121 --> 01:19:53,623
<font color="#787878">It's Sam's turn.</font>

952
01:19:59,712 --> 01:20:02,181
<font color="#787878">Peter, just go.</font>

953
01:20:02,548 --> 01:20:05,768
<font color="#787878">You have Block's life, you're safe now.</font>

954
01:20:06,635 --> 01:20:08,103
<font color="#787878">Please.</font>

955
01:20:08,345 --> 01:20:10,222
<font color="#787878">I'm sorry, Molly.</font>

956
01:20:12,391 --> 01:20:15,144
<font color="#787878">But you just witnessed the murder
of a federal agent.</font>

957
01:20:17,813 --> 01:20:22,319
<font color="#787878">And I'm not gonna spend
the life I just earned in prison.</font>

958
01:20:33,787 --> 01:20:36,415
<font color="#787878">Molly, go! Go get help!</font>

959
01:21:04,193 --> 01:21:06,571
<font color="#787878">You son of a bitch!</font>

960
01:21:44,608 --> 01:21:47,828
<font color="#787878">Tell Candice I love her.</font>

961
01:21:48,195 --> 01:21:49,242
<font color="#787878">Peter.</font>

962
01:22:15,180 --> 01:22:18,354
<font color="#787878">It's gone. You killed him.</font>

963
01:22:19,184 --> 01:22:20,982
<font color="#787878">So does that mean I get Block's life?</font>

964
01:22:25,983 --> 01:22:27,485
<font color="#787878">Yeah.</font>

965
01:22:28,193 --> 01:22:30,070
<font color="#787878">I guess I do.</font>

966
01:22:46,044 --> 01:22:47,546
<font color="#787878">Do you mind if I take the window seat?</font>

967
01:22:47,963 --> 01:22:51,012
<font color="#787878">~ You're gonna make me sit in the middle?
~ Uh-huh.</font>

968
01:22:51,175 --> 01:22:53,348
<font color="#787878">~ I'm like twice your size.
~ Not really.</font>

969
01:22:53,510 --> 01:22:55,512
<font color="#787878">~ All right.
~ Sit down.</font>

970
01:22:55,679 --> 01:22:58,023
<font color="#787878">~ I'll remove him.
~ Fuck you. I'll remove myself.</font>

971
01:22:58,182 --> 01:22:59,399
<font color="#787878">Get off him!</font>

972
01:22:59,558 --> 01:23:00,810
<font color="#787878">Settle down!</font>

973
01:23:00,976 --> 01:23:03,855
<font color="#787878">~ Come on, Browning! Come on, you punk!
~ Get off the plane!</font>

974
01:23:04,021 --> 01:23:06,490
<font color="#787878">Get off the plane. You don't understand!</font>

