986
01:24:26,228 --> 01:24:28,151
<font color="#787878">Said he had some kind of vision.</font>

987
01:24:29,022 --> 01:24:30,365
<font color="#787878">No.</font>

988
01:24:32,484 --> 01:24:33,576
<font color="#787878">Oh, my God!</font>

989
01:24:38,490 --> 01:24:39,537
<font color="#787878">Sam.</font>

990
01:25:08,186 --> 01:25:09,312
<font color="#787878">I got you!</font>

991
01:25:11,523 --> 01:25:14,447
<font color="#787878">~ Sam!
