01:25:19,114 --> 01:25:20,787
<font color="#787878">No!</font>

994
01:25:45,140 --> 01:25:46,687
<font color="#787878">Nice of you to come, Nathan.</font>

995
01:25:46,850 --> 01:25:49,103
<font color="#787878">I know Roy
