01:25:51,730 --> 01:25:53,858
<font color="#787878">I still can't believe he's gone, though.</font>

998
01:25:54,024 --> 01:25:56,493
<font color="#787878">Yeah. Yeah, no kidding.</font>

999
01:25:56,652 --> 01:25:57,904
<font color="#787878">I guess it was for the best.</font>

1000
01:25:59,404 --> 01:26:00,405
<font color="#787878">What do you mean?</font>

1001
01:26:00,572 --> 01:26:03,746
<font color="#787878">Company did an autopsy
for insurance purposes.</font>

1002
01:26:03,909 --> 01:26:07,004
