01:26:10,582 --> 01:26:12,926
<font color="#787878">Nothing lasts forever but the....</font>

1005
01:26:13,085 --> 01:26:14,712
<font color="#787878">Any day?</font>

1006
01:26:15,671 --> 01:26:16,718
<font color="#787878">Life's a bitch.</font>

1007
01:26:16,880 --> 01:26:18,678
<font color="#787878">Dust in the wind</font>

1008
01:27:59,107 --> 01:28:02,361
